{"tid":349291,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"男人就係賤","createTime":"2017-08-06T12:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T19:41:22.000Z","uid":52542,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b05a3660a29a47b0676e7fceebcd06ca759869d7","tid":349291,"uid":52542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:30:30.000Z","msg":"唔好以為你身邊嗰個唔聲唔聲對你好好咁<br />\nwhatsapp一係emoji，一係字都唔打last seen<br />\n得閒就同啲fd喺telegram搵j圖<br />\n或者入娘娘group做厹<br />\n<br />\n男人會專一係呃人嘅<br />\n想一得二，乜都想要<br />\n<br />\n係，係我on9以為有人對我好<br />\n以為終於有個人愛惜下我<br />\n其實都係同人做厹，幫兄弟娘娘講説話<br />\n都唔會回首望下屋企個老婆<br />\n<br />\n婚都結埋，先至睇清一個人好可悲<br />\n不過暫時未有bb<br />\n仲有一次可以reboot嘅機會<br />\n可以拋低一切乜都唔理，離開呢個世界 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返工要俾正能量啲病人好辛苦，又要扮無事做嘢<br />\n放左工真係好攰好無心機，唔想返屋企 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原諒我咁軟弱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b346523432c714bf62931e7e3dfaa83fcd0e26c6","tid":349291,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:43:34.000Z","msg":"對唔住老婆我唔敢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d4191a46523e0dcfad4356704b9bd4cd3c8432","tid":349291,"uid":52542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:46:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對唔住老婆我唔敢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔係我老公 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺屋企我唔想講嘢"},{"pid":"2b40e536d83c55b8a6247eed931713a07cfe07ba","tid":349291,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T12:53:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>對唔住老婆我唔敢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔係我老公 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺屋企我唔想講嘢</blockquote><br />\n咁男人都係鍾意大波靚女，就好似打j睇av咁<br />\n同我愛你係無關係你明唔明？"},{"pid"